42:22.200 --> 42:25.169
...crimes for which I,
of all people...

42:25.210 --> 42:27.201
should have _some
understanding.

42:31.280 --> 42:34.272
Is it right to let the
second murderer walk free?

42:39.220 --> 42:40.778
I don't understand
the question.

